      <guid>http://localhost:1313/interface/pappelina-language-selection/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Pappelina, an interior design product company, provides a fun language selection page when you arrive at the site. Pick the hand with the ribbons in flag colors for Sweden for Swedish or UK/US for English. I know this is just a Flash splash page, but it&#39;s functional and a pretty entry page.&lt;/p&gt;
